Ethie Ann RUTHERFORD and B. W. Rutherford v. FIDELITY BANKERS TRUST CO. No. 7772. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit June 28, 1937. W. J. Carter, of Johnson City, Tenn., for appellants.

Before HICKS and ALLEN, Circuit Judges.

HICKS, Circuit Judge.

It is ordered that this cause be reversed and remanded 'to the District Court for the Eastern District of Tennessee, for such orders by that court as may be proper.
